> I think this is a bug in other RSS readers if they drop such posts entirely.

@trwnh I agree, hence why I put this in parentheses. However, having no title is very useless even if a reader supports it. I also think putting the content warning of a post in there makes more sense than *only* having it in the description.

Also, yes, the title may be omitted. Does it hurt for it not to be omitted?

@koutsie the title field is required for the feed/channel itself, not individual items in it.

